defaultcrimed
default by the officer at the scene.  The system tries its best to give an accurate account, and sometimes the numbers of more serious crimes exceed the numbers where they are downgraded.  This is something I am sure the HMI will look at; it is one of the indicators for me.  Finally, I would perhaps mention quickly that if you look at all our no
default&#x2011;
defaultcrimes
